        {
            "name": "Duneshaker Solifugid",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [],
            "text": "The largest solifugids, duneshakers, literally make the terrain around them tremble.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 38",
